# client-manager
Modern Client Management System with PHP/MySQL

![Dashboard Preview](public/assets/images/screenshot.png)

## Features

- **User Management**: Role-based access control (Admin/Staff)
- **Client CRM**: Track clients, companies, and interactions
- **Project Management**: Task tracking with deadlines and statuses
- **Financial Tracking**: Income/expense records with analytics
- **Receipt Generation**: PDF receipts with paid/unpaid statuses
- **Calendar System**: Color-coded deadline tracking
- **Internal Chat**: Real-time messaging between team members
- **Data Export**: CSV/PDF exports for clients and projects
- **Email Notifications**: Registration, verification, and alerts

## Requirements

- PHP 8.0+
- MySQL 8.0+
- Apache/Nginx
- Composer (for dependencies)

## Installation

### Manual Setup

1. Clone repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/client-manager.git
   cd client-manager